data.name: newTumbl DARK
Binarysearch.io Dark Theme
data.description:
Covers most things I was able to see, except the editor. The editor can be changed to dark mode by opening the console and entering the following:

window.ace.edit('ace-editor').setTheme("ace/theme/twilight");

data.name: Twitter - No Image Cropping + Extras
data.description:
Stops twitter from cropping all image thumbnails and instead scales them to fit.

Also removes confirmation messages when you copy links to tweets, and eliminates the empty space on the left of the sidebar.
